uot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;5.78&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;3363,36&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;4352,04&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 36.2776%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 36.2776%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;2023-04-15 20:38:41&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;13.4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;30639,78&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;50836,59&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 36.2776%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 36.2776%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;Time difference in seconds: 31121&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;Total vt: 615359.46&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;Total vt_interpol: 530068.99&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 36.2776%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 36.2776%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 8.35962%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 21.4511%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;Mean: &lt;strong&gt;19.77&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 33.9117%; border-width: 1px; height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;Mean: &lt;strong&gt;17.03&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;If the option step is selected, then a mean value of 19.77 is output for the values from the above table. Without the step option, however, the value is 17.03. The difference is quite stark if the time periods between the values are not taken into account at all. Then the result is 7.84.&lt;br&gt;Step means that an unchanged value of the last time is used for the calculation for the period between two values. Without the option step, on the other hand, the average value between a value at a certain point in time and the value at the following point in time is used for the calculation. Mostly it makes sense to calculate with the vt_interpol. Therefore the option step is not selected in the default setting.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;Archivwerte&quot; class=&quot;mce-item-anchor&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Archive values&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;In contrast to the query of a single archive value, a time period is specified here. Since one would like to make possibly further computations with these values, the dialog offers the possibility of displaying the vt, the vt_interpol and the respective Unix timestamp. Reminder: Period in seconds x value = vt.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/EN/47_5.png&quot; data-mce-src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/EN/47_5.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;More about the columns vt, vt interpolated and Unix timestamp &lt;a href=&quot;Hilfe3.php?Hilfe_ID=21&amp;amp;nreg=0&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;Hilfe3.php?Hilfe_ID=21&amp;amp;nreg=0&quot;&gt;you can learn here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;Hinweis&quot; class=&quot;mce-item-anchor&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;One more hint:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Double-clicking on the value supplied by a DH function shows the corresponding formula. However, there are also a lot of parameters. It is easier if you select the cell and then click on the editor icon in the toolbar. This will open the corresponding dialog for the function.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/DE/47_6.png&quot; data-mce-src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/DE/47_6.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'DH - functies', '&lt;table style=&quot;border-collapse: collapse; width: 550px; height: 137.2px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;border-collapse: collapse; width: 550px; height: 137.2px; border-width: 0px;&quot; border=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DH-functies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meer spreadsheet hulp onderwerpen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Tag_suchen&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;#Tag_suchen&quot;&gt;Zoek tag&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;Hilfe3.php?Hilfe_ID=46&amp;amp;nreg=0&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;Hilfe3.php?Hilfe_ID=46&amp;amp;nreg=0&quot; data-mce-selected=&quot;inline-boundary&quot;&gt;Algemene hulp spreadsheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#aktueller_Wert&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;#aktueller_Wert&quot;&gt;huidige waarde&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;Hilfe3.php?Hilfe_ID=48&amp;amp;nreg=0&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;Hilfe3.php?Hilfe_ID=48&amp;amp;nreg=0&quot;&gt;Menu`s en werkbalk﻿&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Archivwert&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;#Archivwert&quot;&gt;Archiefwaarde&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Mittelwert&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;#Mittelwert&quot;&gt;Gemiddelde waarde&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Archivwerte&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;#Archivwerte&quot;&gt;Archief waarden&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;height: 19.6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 198.733px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Hinweis&quot; data-mce-href=&quot;#Hinweis&quot;&gt;Opmerking&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 325.867px; height: 19.6px; border-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;Tag_suchen&quot; class=&quot;mce-item-anchor&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zoek tag&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Welke DH-functie je ook wilt gebruiken, je hebt altijd een tag nodig. Deze tag moet samen met het pad worden opgegeven. Om het specificeren van de tag te vergemakkelijken, vindt u de optie Zoek tag in het menu DH functies, die het volgende dialoogvenster opent:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_1.png&quot; data-mce-src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_1.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Het is een goede gewoonte om de zoekterm in het zoekvak vooraf te laten gaan door een \\% teken, omdat het pad meestal minder bekend is dan de tag-naam.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;aktueller_Wert&quot; class=&quot;mce-item-anchor&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;huidige waarde&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Deze functie leest de laatste waarde van een tag. Optioneel kunnen ook de eenheid en het tijdstempel worden weergegeven. Gebruik het veld Richting om te bepalen of deze naast of onder de waarde worden weergegeven.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_2.png&quot; data-mce-src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_2.png&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;De tagnaam kan handmatig worden ingevoerd of door te verwijzen naar een cel waarin de tagnaam zich bevindt. In bovenstaand voorbeeld is dat de tag /T25, die zich in cel A1 bevindt. Een klik op de knop naast het invoerveld schrijft het adres van de huidig geselecteerde cel in het veld.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;Archivwert&quot; class=&quot;mce-item-anchor&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Archiefwaarde&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Ook deze functie leest een waarde van een tag uit de DH. In tegenstelling tot de vorige functie worden hier echter wat meer details verwacht. Het gaat om het type van de gewenste waarde. Ruwe waarde betekent dat een waarde wordt ingelezen uit het eerder ingelezen archief. Uurgemiddelde is bijvoorbeeld de gemiddelde waarde van een uur op het opgegeven tijdstip. Vervolgens verwacht de functie een tijdstip voor de waarde. Het zou toeval zijn als een waarde daadwerkelijk op het opgegeven tijdstip was ingelezen. Daarom kan men naast het veld voor het tijdstip kiezen of de waarde het dichtst bij het tijdstip moet worden weergegeven of dat het eerstvolgende tijdstip na het ingevoerde tijdstip moet worden weergegeven. Als alternatief kan ook een geïnterpoleerde waarde op het exact opgegeven tijdstip worden getoond.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_3.png&quot; data-mce-src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_3.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;Mittelwert&quot; class=&quot;mce-item-anchor&quot; contenteditable=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gemiddelde waarde&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;De naam doet het al vermoeden. Een gemiddelde waarde voor een bepaalde periode moet worden weergegeven.&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_4.png&quot; data-mce-src=&quot;Bilder/Hilfe/NL/47_4.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tagnaam, van en tot zijn op de reeds bekende wijze gegeven. De optie stap kan onder bepaalde omstandigheden een aanzienlijke invloed hebben op de gemiddelde waarde.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Een gemiddelde waarde wordt altijd berekend door de DH rekening houdend met de tijdsperioden tussen de onderliggende waarden.&lt;br&gt;Voorbeeld:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table style=&quot;border-collapse: collapse; width: 820px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;border-collapse: collapse; width: 820px; border-width: 1px;&quot; border=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 215.1px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 215.1px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tijdstempel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 52.8833px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 52.8833px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Waarde&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 181.533px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 181.533px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;vt (Tijdsverschil x waarde)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 320.683px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 320.683px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;vt_interpol (Tijdsverschil x gemiddelde waarde)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 215.1px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 215.1px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;2023-04-15 12:00:00&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 52.8833px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 52.8833px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;24.34&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 181.533px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 181.533px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 320.683px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 320.683px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-mce-bogus=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 215.1px; border-width: 1px;&quot; data-mce-style=&quot;width: 215.1px; border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;2023-04-15 18:03:24&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;width: 52.8833px; border-width